CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 12, 1959, pg. A3 reads: "Church Group Helps Kay Club - Aiding Kay Boys Club to get ready for its holiday activities is the Mount Lebanon Presbyterian Church Youth Fellowship, which is under the supervision of the Rev. Harry T. Adamson. During the past weeks members of this group have spent their Saturdays completing toys to be given to members attending Christmas parties at Kay Boys Club. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group of Mount Lebanon Presbyterian Church Youth Fellowship members,  gathered around table making toys for Kay Boy's Club Christmas parties
